#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) Capital punishment is a controversial subject as well . How would you handle it ?
#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : I support capital punishment ; however something more needs to be done to insure that the wrong person does not die .
#Text=More safeguards must be put in place .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) As president , would you try to limit government presence in people 's lives ?
#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : Yes ; lower taxes and less government .
#Text=We need a lot less government in our face ; and less taxes to support big government which is way too powerful .
#Text=I would cut the federal government in many areas .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) How would you handle homosexual marriages ?
#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : This is a state issue and the federal government has no Constitutional right to get involved in this issue .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) How would you handle the environment ?

#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : I would be the best president this nation has had in regards to the environment since President Teddy Roosevelt ; I rank him right up their in high regards next to George Washington and Thomas Jefferson .
#Text=Great Men .
#Text=We can greatly reduce our dependence on foreign gas and oil by ' burning ' clean fuel .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) What exactly does the Constitution Party stand for ?
#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : The Constitution and the Bill of Rights ; go to their web site and read their ( our ) platform .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) Why do you think it is necessary that a third party candidate be voted into the White House this year ?

#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : End the wars , Save Social Security ; I am on a Constitution Party national committee dealing with Social Security and our committee has a very good plan to not only save Social Security , but keep it well for 100 years ; get it out of the hands of Congress which has robbed it .
#Text=I will also end the taxation of ALL Social Security benefits for those that are retired and eliminate the earnings requirement .
#Text=I will also end free trade and bring good quality , high paying jobs back top the USA with good health benefits .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) Do you think you have a good shot at winning the Constitution Party nomination ? If so , do you think it is really possible to win the general election ?
#Text=Lt. Colonel Riekse : I will know Saturday the 26th if I win the nomination of the Constitution Party .
#Text=As to wining the general election , I 'm very sure that I will do far better then we have done in the previous 20 years as a ' third ' party .
#Text=I 'm not only more qualified to be commander in chief then either the Democrat or Republican , but will be far better for the country .

#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) We have n't seen many Max Riekse billboards , commercials or television appearances . Will we if you win the Constitution Party nomination ? Or are you trying to have a more grassroots campaign ?
